"22:5:60" : {s: 22, a: 5, w: 60, r: "نزل", t: "أَنزَلْنَا", l: "أَنزَلَ", lc: 183, tl: "anzalnā", lb: "অবতীর্ণ করা",e: "We send down", b: "আমরা নাযিল করেছি", i: "Kami turunkan", f: 25, rm: "to descend, come down, go down, happen, alight at, settle in a place, lodge. anzala - to send down, give. nazulun - that which is prepared for a guests entertainment, abode, gift. manzil - mansion, station. nazzala - to cause to descend, send down. tanziil - sending down, divine revelation, orderly arrangement and authentic compilation, gradual revelation.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٤ وضمير متصل ", eg: "Verb Perfect 4th form and Pronoun suffix ", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(IV)", deg: "1", gen: "", num: "P", mood: "", lu: "أَنزَلَ،أُنزِلَ،نَزَّلَ،تَنزِيلٌۭ،تَنزِيلُ،مُنَزَّلٌۭ،مُنزِلُونَ"},
